lution couple of the FBODE\nsystem and the regularity assumptions on the coefficient functions, with which\nwe can further deduce that this value function and its linear functional\nderivative satisfy the Bellman and master equations, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 May 2023 17:40:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-22"}
