 to be more efficient in learning value function\napproximations for larger and more complex problem settings than the ADP\napproach. However, for smaller settings, ADP is shown to outperform NeurADP.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 May 2023 22:49:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-23"}
